question: Please provide names of the patients that are linked with the organization ROYAL OF FAIRHAVEN NURSING CENTER.
answers:
SELECT DISTINCT p.first, p.last 
FROM patients p 
LEFT JOIN payer_transitions pt ON p.id=pt.patient 
LEFT JOIN payers py ON pt.payer=py.id 
LEFT JOIN providers pr ON py.provider=pr.id 
LEFT JOIN organizations org ON pr.organization=org.id 
WHERE org.name='ROYAL OF FAIRHAVEN NURSING CENTER';

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT m.id) 
FROM payers p 
LEFT JOIN payer_transitions pt ON p.id=pt.payer 
LEFT JOIN patients pa ON pt.patient=pa.id 
LEFT JOIN claims c ON pa.id=c.patient 
LEFT JOIN claims_transactions ct ON c.id=ct.claim 
LEFT JOIN medications m ON ct.medication=m.id 
WHERE p.id='d31fccc3-1767-390d-966a-22a5156f4219';
